<hymn_number>1213</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 rén de yī shēng xū kōng yòu duǎn zàn, qū zhǐ shù suàn hái néng yǒu duō shǎo nián.
 zài shì yī tiān yào gǎn xiè zhǔ ēn diǎn, cì fú yī rì sān cān bái tiān hé yè wǎn.
 gǎn xiè tiān fù gěi wǒ shēng mìng yǔ shí jiān, gǎn xiè tiān fù gěi wǒ qīn rén hé tóng bàn.
 wǒ men yào zhēn xī měi yī cì tuán jù, bǐ cǐ dài qiú bǐ cǐ quàn miǎn bǐ cǐ zhù yuàn.</lyrics>
<title>rén de yī shēng 迦南1213</title>
</song>